      "markdown": "如：My.pen is much more expensive than yours.(我的笔你的\n\n\n\n## (3) 周名、月名和季节名前一般不用\n\n如：He was born onMonday，Februa181995.他生在1995年日星期一)\n\n\n\n(4)(第一次使用)复数名词表示人或事物的类别时不用。如：Men are cleverer than monkeys.(人比猴聪明.)\n\n## (5) 三餐饭前不用\n\n如:We have breakfast at home and lunch at school.(我们在家吃早饭，在梭吃午饭)\n\n\n\n## (6) 节、假日前一般不用\n\n如：Onhildrens Dytheboyofngtpreentfrom theirprents.(在儿童节，这些男孩经常得到父母的礼物)\n\n\n\n## (7) 球类名词前不用\n\n如：The children play footba on Saturday afternoons.(孩子们星期六下午踢足球.)\n\n\n\n(8)城市的重要/主要建筑物名称前不用.\n\n如：They are now at People's Cinoma.(他们此刻在人民电影院)\n\n## (9) 一些习惯用语中不用\n\n如：①at/to/from/out of/afterfor school；②ontopof；③in/to/for/after class；④in/to/out ofinto bed;⑤after /at/from /out of /to work；⑥ go to school/bed;①onshow/displayduwtch；i fn of；⑨ at/to sea； in fout of hospital;① in/from down /to town; ② at all; atfrom home；on/in time；⑤atfirtlastonce;afo/brfs/tk ",
